@JamesRTaylor Thanks for your comments. I added two further commits:

199c389: This addresses your comment about the byte array comparison. You were right! I must have got confused earlier with what was being displayed on sqlline.py not matching the sort order.  I also added a formatter for PVarBinary because without it you simply get a Java hash code in sqlline.py which is hard to do anything with.

8cc2b5c: This adds the end-to-end tests you mentioned and also changes the unit test to use the hex representation of the byte array to make it easier to read.

